RPC-ExtDirect-Server version 0.01
=================================

This module provides minimal implementation of Ext.Direct capable server
in pure Perl. It can be used for testing Ext.Direct Actions written in Perl,
or as basis for application server to use in production environment.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

RPC::ExtDirect, CGI::ExtDirect, HTTP::Server::Simple, JSON,
Attribute::Handlers.

